works.description: We have seen some of the luxurious automotive sculptures made using life-sized models, including the including the Piaggio Aero’s private jet sculpture, besides the luxurious automotive sculptures including Mercedes Benz stunning ‘Asthetics 125’ sculpture, and the golden Aston Martin DB5 by Swiss artist Dante. The latest is papercraft model of the Audi A7 by designer Taras Lesko. The papercraft Audi is made using 285 sheets of paper and is the largest papercraft model of a vehicle ever produced
